Colombia's cost living index rise 2.71 pct March 2.03 pct increase February 2.21 pct rise March 1986 government statistic institute said. The result brought year-on-year inflation 20.36 pct compare 22.65 pct end-March 1986 19.77 pct end February 1987. The government predict inflation slightly low 1986 reach 20.9 pct. REUTER 